{"tid":1779779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【風雲人物】小特朗普轟《時代》離棄香港抗爭者 前比利時首相：我選香港民主示威者","createTime":"2019-12-12T01:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T06:31:29.000Z","uid":147522,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7558e6a5d851983e2043205415925661d51bca18","tid":1779779,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"瑞典16歲環保少女環保少女通貝里（Greta Thunberg）獲選為美國《時代》周刊2019年度風雲人物，特朗普長子唐納德（Donald Trump Jr.）批評《時代》離棄（leaves out）香港抗爭者，比利時前首相也在Twitter發文，稱個人會選擇香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n唐納德在Twitter發文說：「《時代》離棄那些為自己性命和自由而戰的香港示威者，去推銷一個被用作營銷噱頭的少女。你們怎敢這麼做？」唐納德用了通貝里9月在聯合國氣候行動峯會上，嚴厲譴責各國領袖的名言「你們怎麼敢這麼做」（How dare you），來反擊《時代》周刊。<br />\n<br />\n此外，比利時前首相、歐洲議會議員伏思達（Guy Verhofstadt）亦發文說，他個人會選擇香港爭取民主的示威者做年度風雲人物，不過認為通貝里也值得獲頒這個頭銜，他希望這有助將氣候危機的訊息傳播開去。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》編輯今年選出通貝里為年度風雲人物，不過解釋選擇通貝里的理據時，也兩度提及香港，指她代表新一代自己危機自己救的時代精神。"},{"pid":"b21a9657df6e183fcd3ec6526324bfb300349dbe","tid":1779779,"uid":251945,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:52:08.000Z","msg":"輸左比贏好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7d00575968d3e26e7b623ff20c22e75243d29e","tid":1779779,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【第十柒期牆紙】起來，不願做奴隸的人們<br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnANT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=08cf83a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnANT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=ccbd80db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1778521/page/1